title: Redeem your skin (Oceania) unable to subscribe to YouTube and Twitter
body: As it says in the title, I was not able to subscribe too the YouTube channel as it would not let me log onto my account through the website. With twitter i actually got the code through following them but when the code was applied it was not accepted. Has anyone had any trouble with this or have a solution?

replies.body:
Hey Cookieeee,

Chances are that you're using the instructions for the wrong region. For the free content available to OCE, check out the [**Promotional Content**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/202083184-Promotional-Content-Free-Swag-) (Free Swag) Riot Games Support article. Keep in mind that Unchained Alistar is not available as a free skin for the OCE region at this time.
